<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="PixelNest FAQ - Frequently Asked Questions">
    <title>FAQ - PixelNest</title>
    
    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/assets/img/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/img/favicon.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/assets/img/favicon.png">
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
    <script src="/js/theme-manager.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="text-white">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <main class="mt-20">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="section-container relative z-10">
                <div class="text-center mb-16">
                    <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 glass rounded-full text-xs font-mono font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6 text-violet-400">
                        Support
                    </span>
                    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight">
                        Frequently Asked Questions
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                        Find answers to common questions about PixelNest
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ Categories -->
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
                    <!-- General -->
                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">General Questions</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-violet-400">What is PixelNest?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">PixelNest is an AI-powered platform that allows you to generate high-quality images and videos from text descriptions. We use state-of-the-art AI models to bring your creative visions to life in seconds.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-violet-400">Do I need technical skills to use PixelNest?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">No technical skills required! Our platform is designed to be user-friendly. Simply describe what you want to create, choose your settings, and let our AI do the work.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-violet-400">What can I create with PixelNest?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">You can create images, edit photos, upscale images, remove backgrounds, generate videos, convert images to videos, and much more. Our platform supports various AI models for different creative needs.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Pricing & Credits -->
                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">Pricing & Credits</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-fuchsia-400">How does the credit system work?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Credits are used to generate content. Each generation consumes credits based on the AI model, resolution, and duration (for videos). You can purchase credits in packages that never expire.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-fuchsia-400">Do credits expire?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">No! Your credits never expire. Use them whenever you need them, at your own pace.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-fuchsia-400">How much do credits cost?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">We offer various packages starting from 50,000 IDR for 100 credits. Larger packages provide better value. Check our <a href="/pricing-page" class="text-violet-400 hover:text-violet-300">pricing page</a> for details.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-fuchsia-400">What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">We accept bank transfers, e-wallets (GoPay, OVO, DANA), and credit cards through our secure payment partner Tripay.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-fuchsia-400">Can I get a refund?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Credits are non-refundable once purchased. However, if you experience technical issues or problems, please contact our support team and we'll help resolve them.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Content & Usage -->
                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">Content & Usage</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-blue-400">Who owns the content I create?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">You own all rights to the content you generate on PixelNest. You can use it for personal or commercial purposes without restrictions.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-blue-400">Can I use generated content commercially?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Yes! All content you create can be used for commercial purposes including marketing, products, websites, and more.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-blue-400">Are there any content restrictions?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Yes. We prohibit illegal, harmful, offensive, or adult content. Content that infringes on intellectual property rights is also not allowed.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-blue-400">How long are my creations stored?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Your creations are stored securely in your gallery. You can download them anytime. We recommend downloading important files for backup.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Technical -->
                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">Technical Questions</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-purple-400">What AI models do you use?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">We use leading AI models including Veo 2, Sora 2, FLUX, Stable Diffusion, and more. Each model has different strengths for various creative tasks.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-purple-400">How long does generation take?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Most images generate in 10-30 seconds. Videos typically take 1-5 minutes depending on duration and complexity.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-purple-400">What file formats are supported?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Images are delivered in PNG or JPG format. Videos are delivered in MP4 format, compatible with all major platforms.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-purple-400">Can I use the API?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">API access is available for Enterprise customers. Contact our sales team for more information.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Account & Support -->
                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">Account & Support</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-pink-400">How do I create an account?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Click "Sign Up" and register with your email or Google account. Verification is instant and you can start creating immediately after purchasing credits.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-pink-400">I forgot my password. What do I do?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Click "Forgot Password" on the login page. We'll send you a reset link to your registered email address.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-pink-400">How can I contact support?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">You can reach us through our <a href="/contact" class="text-violet-400 hover:text-violet-300">contact page</a> or email us at support@pixelnest.id. We respond within 24 hours.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-pink-400">Can I delete my account?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-300">Yes, you can request account deletion by contacting our support team. Note that unused credits will be forfeited upon deletion.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Still Have Questions -->
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12">
                    <div class="glass-strong rounded-2xl p-12 text-center">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight">Still Have Questions?</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">Our team is here to help you succeed</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary px-8 py-3">Contact Support</a>
                            <a href="/documentation" class="btn-outline px-8 py-3">View Documentation</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>

